        <item>
            <title>NBA 引入 AI 机械人，Stephen Curry 率先体验智能射波训练</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/17/nba-ai-robots-training/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nba-ai-robots-training</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/17/nba-ai-robots-training/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 05:38:41 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[nba]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1291632</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>NBA 于盐湖城展示最新 AI 机械人技术，并邀请金州勇士队球星 Stephen Curry 率先试用。Stephen Curry 在训练时使用名为 ABE（Automated Basketball Engine） 的机械人作为投篮伙伴，ABE 机械人可以自动执波、亦设有精准传球功能，使球员能全神贯注于投篮训练。Stephen Curry 最初对这项高科技设备感到新奇，但旋即适应，并认为表示机械人无须饮水休息，可以帮助球员进行更加高强度的训练。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1292070 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Stephen Curry 使用 ABE 机械人协助训练，图片来源：<a href="http://youtube.com/watch?v=iwp7HbfNsp4&amp;ab_channel=NBA">NBA@YouTube</a></p><p>Golden State Warriors 主教练 Steve Kerr 亦引入 MIMIC（Motion &amp; Intercept Modular-Interface Coordination） 机械人，协助球员模拟比赛中的进攻与防守战术。这款机械人可精确追踪球员的细微动作，模仿防守者的压迫感，并即时提供反馈，让教练团队得以因应情境调整战术，强化球员临场应变能力。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292071" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲MIMIC，图片来源：<a href="http://youtube.com/watch?v=iwp7HbfNsp4&amp;ab_channel=NBA">NBA@YouTube</a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292072" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲MIMIC 可在训练期间模拟人类球员进攻、防守等动作，图片来源：<a href="http://youtube.com/watch?v=iwp7HbfNsp4&amp;ab_channel=NBA">NBA@YouTube</a></p><p>NBA 透过今次机械人技术测试，展现人工智能于体育领域的潜力。随着技术持续发展，球员与教练团队或许能在不久将来见证更多 AI 投入训练与比赛分析，进一步提升球场表现，为篮球运动开启新篇章。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_71080"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/iwp7HbfNsp4?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://interestingengineering.com/innovation/basketball-robot-stephen-curry-shooting-partner">Interesting Engineer</a>、<a href="https://www.techspot.com/news/106788-stephen-curry-new-shooting-partner-robot-never-gets.html">Tech Spot</a>、 <a href="https://technology.inquirer.net/140724/nba-debuts-ai-robots-as-stephen-currys-shooting-partner">Technology Inquirer</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
